OV: Take metro line D from Rotterdam Central Station to De Akkers or E to Slinge. Step out at when you arrive at Beurs. And walk 400 meters in the direction of De Kamer van Koophandel, at the side of the water directed to the south.

Car: Drive from the south over the Erasmugbrug or from the north via the Coolsingel towards the cube houses. To do this you need to turn right onto the Posthoornstraat and then the second right onto Wijnhaven.

Maastunnel (partly) closed: From the 3rd of July until the end of September, the tunnel is being renovated. The result is that until then there will be only one tunnel open for motorized traffic from the south to the north. The Maastunnel is closed from the north to the south.
